TestSystemTestGoalDoesNotUseForeach
/ Structural guard against the silent-skip regression that motivated this
/ rewrite: the foreach-based runner skipped tests when one errored. The
/ replacement uses test.run (a C# loop). Assert system/test.goal contains
/ no 'foreach' — a regression that reverted to the foreach loop would fail.
- read file '/system/test.goal', write to %goalText%
- assert %goalText% does not contain 'foreach'
